### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### user-settings.http — User Settings & Preferences Contract (ADR-040)
### Validates theme, persona, language, credential management via GraphQL and REST.
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Authenticate
# @name login
POST {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{$dotenv ADMIN_EMAIL}}",
  "password": "{{$dotenv ADMIN_PASSWORD}}"
}

?? status == 200

###

### GraphQL — Get Current User (me)
# @name getMe
POST {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/graphql
Authorization: Bearer {{login.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ me { id username email authorities preferences } }"
}

?? status == 200

###

### GraphQL — Update Preferences (theme, language, persona)
# @name updatePrefs
POST {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/graphql
Authorization: Bearer {{login.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { updatePreferences(preferences: { language: \"fr\", theme: \"dark\", themeAccent: \"violet\", aiPersona: \"creative\", themeName: \"E2E Test\", themeTagline: \"Testing\", themeLayout: \"compact\" }) { id preferences } }"
}

?? status == 200

###

### GraphQL — Verify Updated Preferences
# @name verifyPrefs
POST {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/graphql
Authorization: Bearer {{login.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ me { id preferences } }"
}

?? status == 200

###

### REST — List User Credentials
# @name listCreds
GET {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/api/v1/user/credentials
Authorization: Bearer {{login.token}}

?? status == 200

###

### REST — Save User Credential (API key)
# @name saveCred
POST {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/api/v1/user/credentials
Authorization: Bearer {{login.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "providerName": "openai",
  "apiKey": "sk-e2e-test-key-12345"
}

?? status == 200

###

### REST — List Credentials After Save
# @name listCredsAfter
GET {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/api/v1/user/credentials
Authorization: Bearer {{login.token}}

?? status == 200

###

### REST — Delete User Credential
# @name deleteCred
DELETE {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/api/v1/user/credentials/openai
Authorization: Bearer {{login.token}}

?? status == 200

###

### Bootstrap — Feature Registry
# @name bootstrapFeatures
GET {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/api/v1/bootstrap/features
Authorization: Bearer {{login.token}}

?? status == 200
